title: NFL ATL: Week 8 TNF Preview, Greg Cosell
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 8 TNF Preview, Greg Cosell
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling preview the Week 8 “Thursday Night Football” matchup between the Carolina Panther and Tampa Bay Buccaneers. NFL Films senior producer Greg Cosell joins the show to shed some light on the 2013 season. Also, Dave Dameshek stops by Studio 66 to squash the beef and challenge Chris Wesseling. Find out which team the heroes ‘stick a fork in’ this week. Lastly, find out if Wesseling keeps or gives up his toaster in ‘Win Wess’ Toaster.’ Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL
